  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Main] Delete 1 of your opponent''s Digimon with 11000
    DP or less. If you have a Digimon in play with [Omnimon] or [Greymon] (other
    than [DoruGreymon], [BurningGreymon], or [DexDoruGreymon]) in its name, delete
    1 of your opponent''s Digimon with 15000 DP or less instead.'
